Con prisa.

00:16:53.270 --> 00:16:54.150
No me eches.

00:16:55.780 --> 00:16:57.030
Qué persona más mala y arrogante.

00:16:57.660 --> 00:16:58.230
Ya.

00:17:09.380 --> 00:17:10.030
Venga.

00:17:11.470 --> 00:17:12.780
Date prisa.

